      "rdf:value": "<L>25983<pc>149,2<k1>Ar<k2>Ar<h>1<e>1\r\n<hom>1.</hom> <s>Ar</s> ¦ <ab>cl.</ab> 4. <ab>P.</ab> <s>A/ryanti</s>, to praise, <ls>RV. viii, 16, 6</ls> and <ls n=\"RV.\">x, 48, 3</ls> (perhaps connected with √ <s>f</s>). <info whitneyroots=\"Ar,6\"/><info verb=\"genuineroot\" cp=\"4P\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
